com.amplifyframework.datastore.appsync

Class AppSyncExtensions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amplifyframework.datastore.appsync.AppSyncExtensions

  • public final class AppSyncExtensions
extends java.lang.Object
    Model representing a AppSync specific extensions map. This data may be included on a GraphQLResponse.Error object, and is represented as a Map<String, Object>. This class can be used to create a strongly typed model by passing the Map<String, Object> to the constructor.
